#

Pineapple Teriyaki Salmon

$15.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

SeafoodQuickHealthy

Description

A sweet and savory salmon dish with a tropical twist, perfect for a quick yet gourmet dinner.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillets: 4 (6 oz)
  • Pineapple juice: 1/2 cup
  • Soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Honey: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • Ginger, grated: 1 tablespoon
  • Pineapple rings: 4
  • Green onions, sliced: 2
  • Sesame seeds: 1 tablespoon
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
